# Basic keybinds

## Just for test
alt + z
	notify-send Im_ork

##~~~~~~~~~~reload config~~~~~~~~~~

## Make sxhkd reload it's configuration file
alt + r
	kill `pgrep sxhkd` && sxhkd &

##~~~~~~~~~~program stuptup~~~~~~~~~~

## Program launcher
alt + x
	dmenu_run

## Unicode simbold to clipboard
super + shift + u
	dmenuunicode

## Open Firefox
super + shift + f
	firefox

## Start terminal emulator
super + shift + Return
	gnome-terminal

##~~~~~~~~~~power supply~~~~~~~~~~

## Power off
super + shift + BackSpace
	prompt "Are you sure shutdown PC?" "shutdown now"
	

## Reboot
super + ctrl + shift + BackSpace
	prompt "Are you sure reboot PC?" "shutdown -r now"

## Suspend
shift + BackSpace
	prompt "Are you sure suspend PC?" "systemctl suspend"